nt velocity 向下跌。由於佢air resistance 好細，所以我地可以得佢balance air resistance 個force 都好細，hence 個terminal velocity 都好細。<br />\n<br />\n由於m 同v 都好細<br />\n跌落地既impact 都好細。<br />\n<br />\n一開頭我話睇impact, 其實仲要睇埋佢承受既壓力 <br />\np=F/A<br />\n個force 我地可以簡單地當佢係W=mg W好細<br />\np=W/A<br />\n網上資料，一隻螞長3mm,闊1mm(1/3 唔緊要，知道佢係mm做單位）所以佢既area 係 10^-6 <br />\n重量係milligram 都係*10^-6<br />\n計返都係1個大氣壓力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以佢唔會跌死，都唔會爆"},{"pid":"b9c56ebe3a75a13c04afe7352d7adadf4cabfda0","tid":596033,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77bc4d32fe720115deda80b60c804ecc5bde4e09","tid":596033,"uid":82829,"like":7,"dislike":166,"score":-159,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"F=ma<br />\nmase細嘅話個Force都唔大得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0833c03be11a78adf3a40a3b79ca3724a2aea1","tid":596033,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"306b87286ddd750bba278a033163a65824a0bd5d","tid":596033,"uid":30808,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"成班中學雞喺到拋書包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3682275a4ced55f2823f61be1982d3064fcccaa3","tid":596033,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下答先<br />\n<br />\n睇佢會唔會死，要睇下個impact 係幾大<br />\np=mv <br />\n同mass 同velocity 有關<br />\nmass 好細，暫時唔睇<br />\n因為uniform area 細，所以個air resistance <span style=\"color: red;\">細</span>，<br />\n但同時f=ma 同埋v=u+at既關係, 佢既velocity 越來越大，而v越大，air resistant 又越大，直到air resistance 同 向下加速既force 相同既時候，佢會係以constant velocity 向下跌。由於佢air resistance 好細，所以我地可以得佢balance air resistance 個force 都好細，hence 個terminal velocity 都好細。<br />\n<br />\n由於m 同v 都好細<br />\n跌落地既impact 都好細。<br />\n<br />\n一開頭我話睇impact, 其實仲要睇埋佢承受既壓力 <br />\np=F/A<br />\n個force 我地可以簡單地當佢係W=mg W好細<br />\np=W/A<br />\n網上資料，一隻螞長3mm,闊1mm(1/3 唔緊要，知道佢係mm做單位）所以佢既area 係 10^-6 <br />\n重量係milligram 都係*10^-6<br />\n計返都係1個大氣壓力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以佢唔會跌死，都唔會爆</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6b94f523682489103d8ee0030d8e38f0003f5bd1","tid":596033,"uid":165980,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔會 但係可被感情摧毀"},{"pid":"9e4dd0462256bb2d83622baaf9a6401f6377cec3","tid":596033,"uid":73410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77bc4d32fe720115deda80b60c804ecc5bde4e09","tid":596033,"uid":82829,"like":7,"dislike":166,"score":-159,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"F=ma<br />\nmase細嘅話個Force都唔大得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"跌唔跌死唔係應該睇momentum嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都有mass細呢個factor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9087ecafdf201e954e5f42b74b3758d9cd5f4a5","tid":596033,"uid":46849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11b4c5d499359a459296728f88424502b43b2507","tid":596033,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7da672dbaeff4eedef20e4849ea2edf6bf2c599a","tid":596033,"uid":124639,"like":134,"dislike":1,"score":133,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f7KSfjv4Oq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff7KSfjv4Oq0&d=VYmZ4YKFRU2EKBODof7%2B0AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3548d33f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f7KSfjv4Oq0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"解釋得好完整<br />\n<br />\nsurface area to volume ratio --&gt; pressure / cushion<br />\nweight / mass<br />\nair